Aunt Peggy standing next to JFK.

33:00.100 --> 33:01.960
作为孩子  这让我觉得很酷
As a kid, that was pretty cool.

33:02.130 --> 33:04.120
但这也是很大的压力
But, it was a lot to live up to.

33:04.370 --> 33:07.230
所以我从不告诉别人我们是亲戚
Which is why I never told anyone we were related.

33:08.270 --> 33:09.360
有一次我问她
I asked her once

33:09.360 --> 33:12.600
在女性饱受歧视的时代
how she managed to master diplomacy and espionage

33:12.600 --> 33:16.560
她是如何成为一名成功的外交官和间谍的
in a time when no one wanted to see a woman succeed at either.

33:17.480 --> 33:19.530
她回答说  能妥协就妥协
She said, compromise where you can.

33:20.230 --> 33:23.230
不能妥协就坚持己见
But where you can't, don't.

33:24.240 --> 33:26.480
即使你身边所有人
Even if everyone is telling you

33:26.480 --> 33:29.850
都把错的说成对的
that something wrong is something right.

33:30.040 --> 33:33.060
即使全世界都叫你让开
Even if the whole world is telling you to move.

33:33.460 --> 33:37.250
你必须如大树般稳稳站住
It is your duty, to plant yourself like a tree,

33:37.380 --> 33:39.370
直视他们的眼睛说  "不...
look them in they eye and say, "No...

33:40.240 --> 33:41.500
你让开"
... you move."

33:53.420 --> 33:54.910
被解冻后
When I came out of the ice,

33:55.610 --> 33:57.420
我以为我认识的人都死了
I thought everyone I had known was gone.

33:58.710 --> 34:00.730
后来知道她还活着
When I found out that she was alive,

34:01.870 --> 34:03.610
只觉得还有她在很幸运
I was just lucky to have her.

34:04.070 --> 34:05.920
有你也是她的幸运
She had you back too.

34:08.150 --> 34:09.360
还有谁签字了
Who else signed it.

34:10.100 --> 34:13.080
托尼  罗德  幻视
Tony, Rhodey, Vision.

34:14.000 --> 34:14.950
克林特呢
Clint?

34:15.800 --> 34:17.310
他说自己退休了
Says he's retired.

34:17.370 --> 34:19.530
-旺达呢  -待定
- Wanda? - TBD.

34:20.810 --> 34:23.700
我要去维也纳签《协议》
I'm off to Vienna for the signing of the Accords.

34:23.700 --> 34:25.610
飞机上还有好多空位
There's plenty of room on the jet.

34:29.260 --> 34:32.110
这虽然是最轻松的路
Just because it's the path of least resistance

34:32.120 --> 34:34.330
不代表就是错的路
doesn't mean it's the wrong path.

34:34.430 --> 34:37.160
团结比团结的方式更重要
Staying together is more important than how we stay together.

34:38.510 --> 34:39.950
那我们要为此放弃什么
What are we giving up to do it?

34:44.860 --> 34:47.870
