I'm sorry, Nat. I can't sign it.

34:49.270 --> 34:50.200
我知道
I know.

34:52.800 --> 34:54.210
那你来干吗
Then what are you doing here?

34:57.100 --> 34:59.000
我不想让你一个人面对
I didn't want you to be alone.

35:06.070 --> 35:06.800
过来
Come here.

35:09.210 --> 35:12.710
<b>维也纳</b>

35:12.670 --> 35:15.390
在一次特殊的联合国会议中
At a special United Nations conference,

35:15.710 --> 35:20.980
117个国家一起正式签署了《索科威亚协议》
117 countries have come together to ratify the Sokovia Accords.

35:25.290 --> 35:26.960
-抱歉  请问是罗曼诺夫小姐吗  -是
- Excuse me, Miss Romanoff? - Yes.

35:26.960 --> 35:28.300
需要您签个字
These need your signature.

35:30.200 --> 35:31.890
-谢谢  -谢谢
- Thank you. - Thanks.

35:32.530 --> 35:35.630
我们俩似乎都不习惯成为焦点人物
I suppose neither of us is used to the spotlight.

35:36.130 --> 35:39.270
毕竟这不总是好事
Well, it's not always so flattering.

35:39.340 --> 35:41.470
你到目前表现得还好嘛
You seem to be doing alright so far.

35:42.360 --> 35:44.620
考虑到你之前在国会山的经历
Considering your last trip to Capitol Hill,

35:44.690 --> 35:48.050
