Please, allow me to apologize for what happened in Nigeria.

36:12.110 --> 36:13.050
谢谢
Thank you.

36:13.840 --> 36:16.110
谢谢你对我们的支持
Thank you for agreeing to all this.

36:16.220 --> 36:19.570
