This assembly is now in session.

36:25.290 --> 36:26.900
未来在召唤我们了
That is the future calling.

36:28.460 --> 36:29.650
很荣幸
Such a pleasure.

36:30.000 --> 36:30.810
谢谢
Thank you.

36:31.990 --> 36:35.990
你不喜欢外交
For a man who disapproves of diplomacy,

36:36.200 --> 36:38.650
却做得越来越好
you're getting quite good at it.

36:38.650 --> 36:40.380
那就好  父亲
I'm happy, Father.

36:45.340 --> 36:46.460
谢谢
Thank you.

36:47.230 --> 36:48.330
谢谢
Thank you.

36:49.000 --> 36:51.620
当失窃的瓦坎达振金
When stolen Wakandan vibranium

36:51.620 --> 36:54.000
被用于制造可怕的武器
was used to make a terrible weapon,

36:54.450 --> 36:58.390
我们瓦坎达人被迫质疑我们的遗产
we, in Wakanda, were force to question our legacy.

36:58.970 --> 37:01.380
在尼日利亚遇害的那些男男女女
Those men and women killed in Nigeria,

37:01.380 --> 37:03.310
是前去开展慈善活动
were part of a good will mission

37:03.320 --> 37:06.080
而他们的祖国已在阴影中待了太久
from a country too long in the shadows.

37:06.920 --> 37:11.100
然而  我们不会因不幸而却步
We will not, however, let misfortune drive us back.

37:11.100 --> 37:14.820
我们会努力让我们想走入的世界更加美好
We will fight to improve the world we wish to join.

37:15.280 --> 37:19.540
我非常感激复仇者联盟对此计划的支持
I am grateful to the Avengers for supporting this initiative.

37:21.190 --> 37:25.210
瓦坎达非常骄傲能为和平贡献力量
Wakanda is proud to extend its hand in peace.

37:25.210 --> 37:26.810
大家卧倒
Everybody get down!

38:01.690 --> 38:04.370
我妈妈曾劝我不要入伍  但是...
My mom tried to talk me out of enlisting, but...

38:04.500 --> 38:05.690
但佩吉姑妈没有
not Aunt Peggy.

38:05.970 --> 38:08.060
我的第一个大腿枪套就是她送的
She brought me my first thigh holster.

38:08.700 --> 38:11.700
-非常实用  -还很时髦
- Very practical. - And stylish.

38:17.600 --> 38:19.800
中情局把你派来了这里吗
The CIA has you stationed over here now?

38:19.800 --> 38:22.040
是去柏林  联合反恐任务小组
At Berlin, Joint Terrorism Task Force.

38:22.040 --> 38:22.870
这样啊
Right.

38:23.510 --> 38:25.650
-听起来不错  -可不是
