39:14.380 --> 39:17.210
冬日战士詹姆斯·布坎南·巴恩斯
as James Buchanan Barnes, the Winter Soldier.

39:17.280 --> 39:18.830
这名臭名昭著的九头蛇特工
The infamous Hydra agent,

39:18.830 --> 39:22.250
与数起恐怖袭击和政治暗杀有牵连
linked to numerous acts of terrorism and political assassinations.

39:22.250 --> 39:23.600
我得去工作了
I have to go to work.

39:29.780 --> 39:30.510
给军情六处打电话
Call MI6

39:30.510 --> 39:32.780
看看能否让微取证小组快速行动
see if we can get Micro Forensics to hurry this up.

39:32.780 --> 39:35.310
两小时内得赶过来  不然就没意义了
We need the whole team here in two hours or it's not worth it.

39:45.830 --> 39:47.020
我非常抱歉
I'm very sorry.

39:53.770 --> 39:58.630
在我的文化里  死亡并不是终结
In my culture, death, is not the end.

40:00.200 --> 40:03.390
更像是  前往陌生领域的起点
It's more of a... stepping-off point.

40:04.430 --> 40:08.060
你向芭丝特与塞赫麦特伸出双手
You reach out with both hands and Bast and Sekhmet,

40:08.160 --> 40:10.570
他们带你走进绿草原  在那里
they lead you into the green veldt where....

40:11.970 --> 40:13.460
你可以永远奔跑下去
you can run forever.

40:15.100 --> 40:16.850
听起来非常安宁
That sounds very peaceful.

40:18.100 --> 40:19.860
我父亲也这样认为
My father thought so.

40:21.930 --> 40:23.730
但是我不是我的父亲
I am not my father.

40:24.370 --> 40:25.370
特查拉
T'Challa.

40:26.090 --> 40:28.920
特遣队会决定谁去抓巴恩斯
Task Force will decide who brings in Barnes.

40:30.850 --> 40:32.560
不用麻烦了  罗曼诺夫小姐
Don't bother, Miss. Romanoff.

40:33.940 --> 40:35.820
