I know how much Barnes means to you. I really do.

40:57.770 --> 40:59.170
待在家里  别出来
Stay home.

40:59.790 --> 41:03.720
你只会让局面更糟  让我们都不好做  求你
You'll only make this worse for all of us. Please.

41:03.720 --> 41:05.610
