- Are you saying you'll arrest me? - No.

41:07.640 --> 41:10.720
如果你出手  会有人抓你的  现在就是这样了
Someone will, if you interfere. That's how it works now.

41:10.940 --> 41:12.570
要是他都变成这样了  小娜
If he's this far gone, Nat,

41:12.970 --> 41:14.260
