I should be the one to bring him in.

41:14.270 --> 41:15.110
为什么
Why?

41:15.260 --> 41:17.430
因为我是最不可能因此丧命的人
Because I'm the one least likely to die trying.

41:20.330 --> 41:21.390
该死
Shit.

41:25.580 --> 41:26.970
她叫你别插手吗
She tell you to stay out of it?

41:29.190 --> 41:31.390
