求你  救命
Please. Help.

02:01:53.710 --> 02:01:54.980
巴恩斯中士
Sergeant Barnes.

02:01:56.400 --> 02:01:57.340
霍华德
Howard.

02:02:05.310 --> 02:02:06.390
霍华德
Howard!

02:02:43.950 --> 02:02:45.180
