You can't beat him hand to hand.

02:09:36.920 --> 02:09:38.380
分析他的攻击模式
Analyse his fight pattern.

02:09:38.780 --> 02:09:39.660
扫描中
Scanning!

02:09:44.190 --> 02:09:45.590
